{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">These drones aren't cheap you know...</h2><br>Get in and get out, hopefully with some scrap for the trouble. The drone probably won't make it, but that's just how things go. <br><br>But don't go poking around too much, you might find more than you bargained for.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About</h2><br>Debris Field is a top down physics based space shooter with rogue-like elements, that focuses on using Newtonian movement to out maneuver swarms of enemies. <br><br>You will have to fight your way through a series of unforgiving arenas, learning to use Newtonian movement to give yourself an edge over your enemies. Upgrade your ship and your weapons along the way whatever you can find, but don't take too long, as the enemy will soon overwhelm you.<br><br>The full game contains:<br><br>    Physics based movement<br>    5 unique levels with different terrain and enemies<br>    Several starting ships, with different stats and loadouts<br>    A dynamic system of incremental stacking upgrades<br>    A persistent difficulty over time system to keep you on your toes<br><br>The Demo contains only the first level, but is otherwise unlimited.<br><br>Follow me on Youtube @BinaryNomadGames for news and development updates<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Thank You!</h2>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Supernova","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/651940/d5afbd96f4c9c767dcf12c9ed8c036b108f7d3df.jpg"},{"name":"Core","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/651940/9b23f7f65e7bda88f0f4c1f98a8f4f51b7ccb54c.jpg"},{"name":"Mining Belt","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/651940/cc4d9de5ffe2c627049b5626bf1e095cda451ecb.jpg"},{"name":"Ice Flow","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/651940/54ad46b6d9034261b0d2cca77fc40d542b06874b.jpg"},{"name":"Infestation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamco